cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL 

This paper is about cross-lingual natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR), which are the main topics of the cs.CL sub-category. The paper also involves machine learning techniques for identifying aligned documents, which falls under the cs.LG and cs.AI sub-categories. Additionally, the paper evaluates the quality of machine translations, which is related to the cs.DL sub-category. Finally, the paper involves web document mining, which is related to the cs.IR sub-category.
